body_html:
In preparation for the ninth confrontation between rival factions Team WALL and Team ALL, ECD's top-secret "Writer" takes an in-depth look at the numbers surrounding this historic feud.

  • 49: total number of individual games throughout eight contests.
  • 26.4: the overall average attendance.
  • 21.3: the average male turnout.
  • 5.1: the average female turnout.
  • 4: number of Wall-All contests scheduled at a seven-event.
  • 3: number of Wall-All contests scheduled at a three-event.
  • 1: the only mid-season showdown Wall-All contest (DODGEBALL 135).
  • 0: number of Wet War Wall-All contests.

    As the old adage goes, "It ain't over 'til it's over!" Participants are urged to mentally and physically prepare for this next battle on November 8 only at DODGEBALL 163! 7:15pm start!
